const RegisterAdmin = () => {
  return (
    <form>
      <label for="username">Username:</label>
      <input
        type="text"
        id="username"
        name="username"
        placeholder="Enter username"
        required
      />

<label for="text">Password:</label>
      <input
        type="password"
        id="password"
        name="password"
        placeholder="Enter password"
        required
      />
      <button type="submit">Add Admin</button>
    </form>
  );
};
export default RegisterAdmin;
